---
// ArquitecturaSistema.astro
import '../styles/arquitectura.css';
---

<section class="arq-root">

  <!-- ── Header ── -->
  <span class="arq-eyebrow">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
      <path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/>
    </svg>
    Servicios
  </span>

  <h2 class="arq-heading">Arquitectura del Sistema: Dos Servicios Independientes</h2>

  <p class="arq-lead">
    Para garantizar claridad técnica y comercial, Ikari se divide internamente en dos grandes
    pilares o servicios autónomos, conectados de forma nativa dentro de la misma plataforma:
  </p>

  <!-- ── Cards ── -->
  <div class="arq-grid">

    <!-- Servicio A: CRM (light) -->
    <div class="arq-card light">
      <span class="arq-card-pill blue">Adquisición Comercial</span>

      <p class="arq-card-label">Marketing y Adquisición</p>
      <h3 class="arq-card-title">SERVICIO A: IKARI CRM</h3>

      <blockquote class="arq-quote">
        "Atraer, nutrir y cerrar nuevas oportunidades de negocio."
      </blockquote>

      <p class="arq-pillars-label">Pilares Técnicos Incorporados</p>
      <ul class="arq-pillars">
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="4"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="22"/>
              <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="4" y2="12"/>
              <line x1="20" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>Captación de Leads</strong>: Formularios integrados y Landing Pages centrales.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87l1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14L2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>Manejo de Embudos</strong>: Trazabilidad visual de prospectos mapeados por etapas.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/>
              <polyline points="3 7 12 13 21 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>Email Marketing</strong>: Automatización de secuencias de nutrición, boletines y seguimientos.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="arq-card-footer">
        <span>Módulo: Compras &amp; Leads</span>
        <span>01 // Ventas Comercial</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Servicio B: Gestión Interna (dark) -->
    <div class="arq-card dark">
      <span class="arq-card-pill green">Rigor Operativo</span>

      <p class="arq-card-label">Operaciones y Administración</p>
      <h3 class="arq-card-title">SERVICIO B: GESTIÓN INTERNA</h3>

      <blockquote class="arq-quote">
        "Estructura interna escalable, control y rigor del día a día."
      </blockquote>

      <p class="arq-pillars-label">Pilares Técnicos Incorporados</p>
      <ul class="arq-pillars">
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>Agenda Interna</strong>: Calendario avanzado cruzando especialistas.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
              <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
              <line x1="9" y1="15" x2="15" y2="15"/>
              <line x1="9" y1="11" x2="15" y2="11"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>CRUD de Pacientes/Clientes</strong>: Control de expedientes e historiales de visitas.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>Multi-Sede &amp; Multi-Doctor</strong>: Registro técnico para múltiples sucursales.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/>
              <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>Finanzas</strong>: Caja de cobro en tiempo real e historial detallado de transacciones.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="arq-pillar">
          <div class="arq-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/>
              <line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="arq-pillar-text">
            <strong>Reportes</strong>: Métricas analíticas claras del rendimiento mensual.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="arq-card-footer">
        <span>Módulo: Columna Operativa</span>
        <span>02 // Operación Clínica</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<script>
    import '../scripts/arquitectura'
</script>